# Meta Layer

> **Apply Intelligently** - What is the meta layer and how it works.

## What is the Meta Layer?

The meta layer is the **mother layer** - a product-agnostic orchestration system that provides the environment for how agents and humans should work together. It's the DNA of any SaaS R&D team.

Think of it as an **AI-native development operating system**.

## Purpose

> **Enable product engineers to create amazing production-ready products using AI.**

The meta layer provides:

- Product-agnostic rules, workflows, and conventions
- Full R&D playbook (not just development - branding, UX, research, etc.)
- Self-improving rules that learn from every feature and bug
- Cognitive scaffold for product engineers
- Context guide for AI agents
- The "womb" (`repos/`) where implementations grow

## The Family Model

```
Meta (Mother) + Feta (Father) = Development Environment
                                      ↓
                            Product Engineer acts here
                                      ↓
                              Implementation (Child)
                              Lives in meta/repos/
```

- **Meta** (Mother): HOW to do things - product-agnostic orchestration
- **Feta** (Father): WHAT to build - product-specific blueprints
- **Implementation** (Child): The actual code, born from Meta + Feta

