## Key Principle

**If you could copy this to a completely different SaaS project and it would still make sense, it belongs in Meta.**

The Meta layer teaches HOW to do any product engineering activity, not WHAT to build.

## Rules vs Commands

| Aspect | Rules | Commands |
|--------|-------|----------|
| **Purpose** | HOW to do things | WHAT + WHERE |
| **Activation** | Always/Intelligently | Manual trigger |
| **Think of as** | Guardrails | Shortcuts |

