## The Product Engineer

The product engineer is the new developer - a full-stack creator who uses the Meta layer's R&D playbook to bring Feta's blueprints to life.

```
Product Engineer = Developer + Designer + Product Manager + Researcher
                   (enabled by AI, guided by Meta, building from Feta)
```

They are the magician of experiences, creating anything by any means necessary in the **correct, validated, agreed-upon way**.

## Self-Improvement

The meta layer learns through:

1. `/reflect` — Compare plan vs outcome
2. `/contribute` — Extract learnings
3. Learnings appended to relevant instruction rules

Each instruction file has a `## Learnings` section that grows over time.

